                        <item xml:id="e1">- The title of the work ፍትሃ፡ ነገስት is crudely written on the front board in large felt-tip pen.&#xD;
- Seal of the parish council of Golʿa Dabra Bǝrhān Yoḥannǝs church: <locus target="#4r">4r</locus>, 116r, 232r.&#xD;
- Crude note written in pen in the upper margin: <locus target="#81v">81v</locus>.&#xD;
